        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/samsa/" class="name">èƒ½å·¥å·§åŒ æ²™é—¨å“¥</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="åŠ›è"></span>

        <span content="2008-11-03" class="main-meta">2008-11-03 10:39:14</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1543989/">è·¯ä¸Šæœ‰æ¸©æš–</a></h2>

